quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  50,1,Qaaf. Mi woondirii Alqur'aanaare teddunde nden
  50,2,"Si ko woni, …ďe Ňčal…óu ko tawi kon jertinoowo arii …ďe iw…óo e ma…ď…ďe ; heefer…ďe …ďen wi'i: \"∆äum …óoo ko huunde haawniinde"
  50,3,"Kere si men maayii, men wontii mbulmbuldi...? ∆äum …óon ko ruttitagol wo…ó…óungol non"
  50,4,Gom…óii Me…óen anndi ko leydi ndin √Īaamata kon e ma…ď…ďe ; hino ka Amen gaa deftere reenunde
  50,5,"Si ko woni, …ďe fennu goonga kan tuma nde ka arunoo e ma…ď…ďe, hi…ďe e nder fiyaaku jil…ďu…óo"
  50,6,"E …ďee ndaaraali kammu ngun dow ma…ď…ďe, ko honno Men mahiri ngun Men cu…óini ngu ; hara per…ói alanaa ngu"
  50,7,"Leydi ndin kadi, Men weerti ndi Men werlii e mayri pelle, Men fu…óini e mayri kala nooneeji [pu…ói] woo…óu…ói"
  50,8,fii tasakuyee e waaju wonannde kala jeyaa…óo ruttotoo…óo
  50,9,"Men jippini kadi ndiyam barkinaa…óam ummaade ka kammu, Men fu…óiniri …óam gese e gabbe so√Īetee…óe"
  50,10,e le…ó…óe tamaro juutu…óe wondu…óe e piindi fawondirndi
  50,11,ko arsike jeyaa…ďe …ďen. Men wuurnitiri …óam kadi leydi yoorundi. Awa ko non woni fii ummital ngal
  50,12,"Ado ma…ď…ďe, yim…ďe nuuhu …ďen, e yim…ďe ∆Āunndu …ďen e Samuuda'en [fow] fennuno"
  50,13,"e 'Aadi'en, e Fir'awna e musi…ó…ďe Luutu …ďen"
  50,14,"e yim…ďe fitaare nden, e yim…ďe Tubba' …ďen. Kala ma…ď…ďe fennuno Nulaa…ďe …ďen, kammbaa Am on jojji"
  50,15,"Kere Men ronkuno fii tagu aranu ngun? Ko woni kam…ďe, hi…ďe e ji…ďaare fii tagiteede laawol kesol"
